This is Debian's prepackaged version of bozomake, Jean-Daniel Pauget's
set of general-purpose utilities for crewing through automaked sources
tree, and more.

The upstream author is the current maintainer for this package :
Jean-Daniel Pauget <bozomake@disjunkt.com>

The upstream source is available at 'http://bozomake.disjunkt.com/'

Upstream Maintainer: Jean-Daniel Pauget <bozomake@disjunkt.com>


